    "description": {
      "zh": "Rifle Dynamics 704 7.62x39 毫米突击步枪是 Rifle Dynamics 公司生产改进版本 AK。其与常规 AK 步枪的主要区别在于 RD 704 枪身前部经过重新设计调整，重心更靠近后方机匣所在位置，大大提高了武器的可控性。",
      "en": "Rifle Dynamics 704 assault rifle 7.62x39mm, an improved version of the AK system manufactured by Rifle Dynamics. The main difference from the standard AK: the design of the front part shifts the center of gravity closer to the receiver, which significantly improves the controllability of the weapon."
